{"tid":1309894,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[宣傳][更新]7.21港島東遊行, 回歸港島戰線","createTime":"2019-07-12T11:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T22:12:52.000Z","uid":240516,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"420fdd1311693f07f9220765df2cf0d6ce82fbbc","tid":1309894,"uid":240516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"[宣傳]7.21港島東遊行, 回歸港島戰線<br />\n<br />\n活動背景: 是次修訂逃犯條例風波中，林鄭月娥得到民建聯、工聯會等建制派大力支持，漠視民意欲強推惡法，引起市民不滿，衍生出源源不斷的警民衝突，更有戰友為此輕生。然而直至今日，政府仍然未能回應市民訴求，林鄭多番改變字眼亦不願明確說出「撤回修例」，為重推惡法留下尾巴。<br />\n<br />\n建制派多年來在港島東區議會中佔據大量議席，但在是次修例中卻未有全面聆聽市民意見，盲目支持政府，加劇社會撕裂，故希望各位街坊能夠再次走出來，以和平遊行的方式向政府以及建制派表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n起步時間: 15:30<br />\n預定路線: 鰂魚涌公園二期-渣華道-英皇道-維園<br />\n途經北角警署, 北角政府合署, 廉政公署總部, 民建聯總部<br />\n(有待不反對通知書確認)<br />\n<br />\n目的: 七大訴求(5+2)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定義<br />\n3. 撤銷對抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 追究黑警暴行，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 落實真雙普選<br />\n6. 承諾不推行社會信用評分制度<br />\n7. 拆除所有監控燈柱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當日19:30民陣將於金鐘舉行集會，主題是要求成立獨立調查委員會，調查連串衝突事件，各位遊行後可以轉移過去集會。"},{"pid":"8bfecde11407c61822b8009d4af0b3fc56bf935c","tid":1309894,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:53:11.000Z","msg":"早啲起步可以接到金鐘個集會?"},{"pid":"76f0f552e0117faa9e2bf09bb086cdf356291492","tid":1309894,"uid":48974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feae69af76571d037be7d68f52fb4c893e4795c7","tid":1309894,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:59:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ff40b12e5fbe8cf97d0c8424fe458a06b2dfb4f","tid":1309894,"uid":278723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:02:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7e0eef6a42a02470e5be735e3b26c989260088b4","tid":1309894,"uid":114579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b61a290d8dafe3dfcf9024d0cb2fe4569cdf61","tid":1309894,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:43:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52e8ecf028ca11ca8a8bbf8bc2d2a163f8169097","tid":1309894,"uid":82223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:46:37.000Z","msg":"聽日光復上水，<br />\n後日沙田野餐，<br />\n7月21重回金鐘！"},{"pid":"a1989f391cfc6ebbdd1197579df9754ad57cb612","tid":1309894,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:50:07.000Z","msg":"之前唔係講西區咩?<br />\n中聯辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2871a3cb706d95eb5296335c955dc96003328fb0","tid":1309894,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T19:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b352ea422edcf9c0aaf941fd46d42d58f6c025","tid":1309894,"uid":274204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T21:08:18.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"764f3fd7ef77d9168d297e04e71ac0424132fa19","tid":1309894,"uid":272942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T21:09:28.000Z","msg":"我聽日光復上水，<br />\n後日去沙田野餐。"},{"pid":"b9f205609301c0a3819ce65f2db9166c56bff23c","tid":1309894,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T21:26:06.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"926c9b400ca2b64f8b3882168d54d7beb34ff882","tid":1309894,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T21:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedc7f8505bdfc5c4fcfcef18476419300be3741","tid":1309894,"uid":159596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-1